    Task

    User Journey through Product Offerings

    As a potential customer exploring solar project solutions,, I navigate through the product offerings to understand the features available for Interconnection Studies and Zoning Ordinances,, so that I can make informed decisions on how SparkHQ's tools can address my specific needs in solar project development.

    Success definition: Given I have accessed the SparkHQ website's product section When I click on the Interconnection Studies link and then the Zoning Ordinances link Then I should see detailed information on Interconnection Studies first, followed by Zoning Ordinances, including relevant visuals and headings that help me understand each topic.
